FBIS4-41834 "drsov124_c_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-124 Daily Report 28 Jun 1994 Federal Assembly Committee Says Agricultural Situation `Catastrophic' Committee Says Agricultural Situation `Catastrophic' LD2806094094 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 0800 GMT 28 Jun 94 LD2806094094 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Russian BFN [From the "Novosti" newscast] [Text] The Federation Council committee for agrarian policy has described the situation in the Russian agro-industrial complex in 1994 as extreme and catastrophic. In its statement it forecasts a production slump in agricultural enterprises of all types of ownership in 1994. It suggests that compared to average annual figures for 1986-90, production will fall by between 45 and 50 percent. The committee believes that in those conditions emergency economic measures are needed to support the agricultural sector.
